Sfizioso Player — licensing
===========================

This repository is licensed by component:

- BSD 2-Clause License — the shared libraries and UI kit:
    src/player_core/   (sfizioso engine wrapper)
    src/core_prefs/    (preference store)
    src/ui-shared/     (React UI kit + C++/JS bridge)
  Full text: LICENSE-BSD-2-Clause.txt

- GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 — the application:
    src/player/        (PlayerProcessor, PlayerEditor, ui/)
  Full text: LICENSE-AGPL-3.0.txt

Bundled dependencies keep their own licenses:

- external/sfizioso — the sfizioso SFZ engine, an independent fork of sfizz,
  BSD 2-Clause. See external/sfizioso/LICENSE.md and external/sfizioso/NOTICE.
- external/JUCE — JUCE, under the JUCE licence (AGPLv3 or commercial). See
  external/JUCE/LICENSE.md.

See NOTICE for attributions.
